{"tid":1015352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女團偶像引退爆內幕　未成年被強迫拍性感照","createTime":"2019-02-10T01:59:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T05:14:39.000Z","uid":147522,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2380c47a269f209b16a9bd6c4f69842f219f1e17","tid":1015352,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T01:59:19.000Z","msg":"日本女團「NMB48」22歲前成員須藤凜凜花，前年在「第9屆AKB人氣總選舉」上突然宣布要結婚並退團搶盡風頭，被認為偶像失格引發爭議，上月更以身心狀況不佳為由，表示要從演藝圈引退，但最近爆出她引退內幕，其實是因為不滿所屬公司安排她走性感路線，曾被公司騙到片場，在沒有事先說明及解釋的情況下拍性感照，當時不到20歲的她（當年規定日本20歲才算成年），被迫挑戰大膽尺度，只能勉強照做，讓她決心離開公司及演藝圈。<br />\n<br />\n此一消息曝光後，有網友表示公司此舉等於逼人「下海」，說須藤凜凜花引退是明智之舉，她去年4月結婚搖身變人妻，嫁圈外男友，表示離開演藝圈後會認真念書，盼如願考上大學，希望朝哲學家的目標努力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wkyTuA4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwkyTuA4.png&h=e731d162&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f306df44779298b31d7274c31ebc5c8077e287fa","tid":1015352,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:01:58.000Z","msg":"得兩張圖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0bc06f03f1544dc95ecbeaf1d610fc1cc2d805b","tid":1015352,"uid":25345,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:16:22.000Z","msg":"咁小事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d538849784ba77b35b217ab1e39b7c570a4593c","tid":1015352,"uid":2223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:19:13.000Z","msg":"有幾性感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3906aa8b815dfbb924023dc3326bf42733e6cb5d","tid":1015352,"uid":74910,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d0bc06f03f1544dc95ecbeaf1d610fc1cc2d805b","tid":1015352,"uid":25345,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:16:22.000Z","msg":"咁小事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:22:37.000Z","msg":"sorry噤錯負皮<img src=\"/assets/